logicalColumns.name: Dist Functional Amount
logicalColumns.description:
CASE WHEN "Line Item Type"   in ('FRT','XXOBJ_PP') THEN 
 "Unit Selling Price" 

ELSE 
CASE WHEN SIGN( "Unit Selling Price"  )=-1 THEN "Unit Selling Price" 
ELSE
EVALUATE('xxoe_utils_pkg.get_price_list_dist(%1,%2,%3)' AS DOUBLE,  "Line Id", "Unit List Price", "Lines"."Attribute4"  
) *  "Quantity" 
*(CASE WHEN    "Average Discount" =100 THEN 0 ELSE (100-"Average Discount"   )/100 END)
END

END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 IN ('FRT', 'XXOBJ_PP') THEN %2 ELSE  CASE  WHEN  SIGN(%2) = -(1) THEN %2 ELSE  EVALUATE('xxoe_utils_pkg.get_price_list_dist(\%1,\%2,\%3)' AS  DOUBLE PRECISION , %3, %4, %5) * %6 *  CASE  WHEN %7 = 100 THEN 0 ELSE (100 - %7) / 100 END  END  END
